{"tid":1897442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係唔係已經放棄左抗爭？","createTime":"2020-02-25T17:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T01:15:13.000Z","uid":40443,"like":22,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bdb474e91141f90d6a476828ad0b8a5f6f383af8","tid":1897442,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"行動po你哋唔推<br />\n成個熱門都係牛丸 打丁 渣波<br />\nIG就個個都講KatieLaw<br />\n啲行動po就開咗幾個鐘頭都冇人睇<br />\n我明白抗爭需要放鬆 食吓花生唔係罪<br />\n但食花生嘅同時可唔可以focus返抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗真係每日都拉緊人<br />\n留意吓被捕人士關注組就知<br />\n成日都有新case要過堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真我好掛住喺街頭抗爭嘅日子<br />\n至少大家都團結一致<br />\n而家慢慢感覺啲人開始冷卻<br />\n我知道時間耐左感覺淡左係好正常<br />\n但可唔可以 <br />\n唔好放棄手足 唔好放棄抗爭<br />\n唔好唔記得被捕嗰7000幾個手足<br />\n唔好唔記得佢哋嘅付出<br />\n唔光復香港點樣救佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好令仲努力緊嘅手足失望 求下你地<br />\n<br />\n推翻行動po先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日有嘢樣你哋要做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n831打死人啊 記唔記得啊 半週年啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897005</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ccc002a7dd58ef5b153cdf42aa70c7de9cd3961","tid":1897442,"uid":40443,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:34:21.000Z","msg":"可唔可以話俾我聽你哋冇放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bab17d4c31768274c05f4756b871bb0c5b6d8d0","tid":1897442,"uid":9193,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:35:08.000Z","msg":"呢排咁多菌仲出嚟遊行開花把撚咩。。"},{"pid":"0af578b59f4f1f85bd9a5420606b07955430debd","tid":1897442,"uid":268519,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"好心啲無營養嘅post直接咪覆啦"},{"pid":"162435943abeb8ab4319f21f8389ba454d58a8bc","ti