"pid":"1034f7f63197e10536d8704a26018c2db8e9bc2f","tid":1897442,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb474e91141f90d6a476828ad0b8a5f6f383af8","tid":1897442,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"行動po你哋唔推<br />\n成個熱門都係牛丸 打丁 渣波<br />\nIG就個個都講KatieLaw<br />\n啲行動po就開咗幾個鐘頭都冇人睇<br />\n我明白抗爭需要放鬆 食吓花生唔係罪<br />\n但食花生嘅同時可唔可以focus返抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班狗真係每日都拉緊人<br />\n留意吓被捕人士關注組就知<br />\n成日都有新case要過堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真我好掛住喺街頭抗爭嘅日子<br />\n至少大家都團結一致<br />\n而家慢慢感覺啲人開始冷卻<br />\n我知道時間耐左感覺淡左係好正常<br />\n但可唔可以 <br />\n唔好放棄手足 唔好放棄抗爭<br />\n唔好唔記得被捕嗰7000幾個手足<br />\n唔好唔記得佢哋嘅付出<br />\n唔光復香港點樣救佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好令仲努力緊嘅手足失望 求下你地<br />\n<br />\n推翻行動po先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日有嘢樣你哋要做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n831打死人啊 記唔記得啊 半週年啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897005</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T00:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QasWSKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQasWSKV.png&h=debe5485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dcSoxKW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdcSoxKW.png&h=6018420f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bbc4ed790d84853436c880746c2bc2743cafee7","tid":1897442,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"349ece66a5b56e55d8624f84b40c6a6c16514122","tid":1897442,"uid":109113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"012e1b089db06375b57cda43435cee9da194b93a","tid":1897442,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"aea7ebe24771a56ae74b288